	door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety There is 
	no elevator. Stairs only to the balcony level. When purchasing ADA accessi
	ble seating\, please feel free to contact us by email or phone if any assi
	stance is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; you may reach 
